website_summaries.verdict: A good silicone accessory set for the most common sizes of air fryers.
pros: Includes a cake pan, pizza pan, skewer rack, metal holder, toast rack, tongs, liners, silicone oil brush, silicone mitts, mat, and muffin cups
Pizza and cake pans are nonstick
cons: Recipe book doesn't really match the products in the set

customer_reviews.title: Fits 6 Qt, sturdy
customer_reviews.text: I want to start by saying I have not used these accessories yet. Check out my photos of how each piece fits inside my 6 quart fryer. (I wanted to show the fit in my Gourmia 6-qt. Stainless Steel Digital Air Fryer, which has an interior of 9 in x 9 in x 4 in). These accessories are of a sturdy, quality material. I won't be able to attest to the non-stick quality or ease of cleaning until I use them. I will update later.
customer_reviews.author: KLA77

customer_reviews.title: High Quality
customer_reviews.text: There are many accessory sets for sale, but this one had many of the things I wanted to use with my 5.3 and 5.8 air fryers. I especially like that the parchment rounds and toast rack were included. The bonus was a nice air fryer cookbook! I give this set an A+++!
customer_reviews.author: Bob

customer_reviews.title: Rust spots after 1st use
customer_reviews.text: Used the cake pan once for a meatloaf in the air fryer. Was fine. Hand washed it AND dried it completely before putting it away. I took it out today to use and there's rust spots everywhere. Return window has now closed a week ago. This is ridiculous considering it was completely dry...
customer_reviews.author: Nicole P.

customer_reviews.title: Great accessories!
customer_reviews.text: I am very happy with my purchase. Everything fits my Chefman Air fryer perfectly and the accessories are great! I can’t wait to make some of the suggested recipes in the cook book. I’ve used the rack, tongs, brush, and liners so far and everything cleaned up nice and easy. The only downside about this purchase experience is I was very confused about when to order. The “in stock” availability status changed daily. Finally after a week of watching I just decided to pre-order and it came in three days, even tho the in stock date was set after that. So you’re reluctant to order based on that, I’d say go for it anyway.
customer_reviews.author: Christine

customer_reviews.title: Fabulous purchase!!!
customer_reviews.text: I am obsessed with this product!!! Having these accessories allows me to no longer have to clean my air fryer after each use. I have an elite premium 5.6 qt air fryer and everything fits perfectly! I would definitely recommend buying this if you use an airfryer often.
customer_reviews.author: Erin

customer_reviews.title: No Disappointment Here
customer_reviews.text: The no-stick surface of these pans are truly no-stick. So far, I've used the cake pan as a casserole and the shallow pan as a loaf pan with the tall wire rack above it to hold our veggies for healthier roasted and spiced veggies instead of boiled and buttered veggies. The recipes I have used have been delicious and with everything that was included I haven't used my regular oven since I got this set because it has everything I need to use my air fryer exclusively!
customer_reviews.author: Joyce Fox

customer_reviews.title: 11 piece FDA 8 inch XL Air Fryer Accessories
customer_reviews.text: These accessories work great in our GoWise Air Fryer. Until we purchased them, we really had no real pans and accessories that would fit in the air fryer. We are pleased to have something that we can not cook and work with in the GoWise air fryer.
customer_reviews.author: Bob Brown

customer_reviews.title: Pans scratch easily!
customer_reviews.text: I was SO disappointed to find out how easily the pans scratch. This morning I fried eggs in the pizza pan, soaked in soapy water and then used a sponge that has a light scratchier on the back. Took finish right off the pan. And why did I pay the same amount as this offering, but get less items? No waffle or sausage mold, no mitts
customer_reviews.author: P.J.

customer_reviews.title: Awesome for use with instant pot.
customer_reviews.text: I bought this mainly so I could make a cake with my instant pot. The included cake pan was perfect, as expected. And the rack-holder-thingy made it easy to get the pan in and out. Everything went through the dishwasher fine—which is make-or-break around here. The included egg maker worked well even though I thought it was silly to break out the instant pot just for eggs. But I made oatmeal at the same time and both things came out perfectly. A few of the accessories were very specific to air fryers, which my instant pot does not do. Still, a great bunch of items to increase the versatility of an instant pot.
customer_reviews.author: Wednesday Lee Friday

customer_reviews.title: No Cookbook
customer_reviews.text: I suppose all these pieces do what they say. I have yet to use them. The description of items includes a cook book which is in reality a 22 page information book that shows the product and then gives some recipes. The only recipe that actually used one of the accessories was the cake. The last four recipes did not match the items in the pictures. My disappointment was in the lack of information about the use of the items and also being told I was getting a cookbook.
